N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6173.7 - Liability

State Regulations

Nothing contained in this Part shall impose liability upon
the division or the State for death, injury, or loss incurred by an eligible
driver by reason of that driver having participated in the Livery Driver Safety

Training Program. Notes
